        "cost_body": "The average person with chronic joint inflammation spends $960-1,800 per year stacking glucosamine, turmeric, fish oil, collagen, and OTC anti-inflammatories — none of which address why inflammatory markers are elevated. When the root cause is bacterial endotoxin leakage from a compromised gut barrier, no downstream supplement resolves it. Origin costs $1.13/day and targets the single upstream mechanism. One capsule replaces the stack.",
